Class Asset

java.lang.Object
Asset
All Implemented Interfaces:
Asset_inter, java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable
public class Asset
extends java.lang.Object
implements Asset_inter
This class stores a unquie asset from the database within a class with each variable corresponding to an important variable within the database regarding that asset type
